      "date": "2011-12-20 06:32:29.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nLooks like failover ability is broken due to powerman issue:\n\n+ pm -h powerman --on client-23vm3\nUsage: powerman [OPTIONS] [TARGETS]\n-1 --on        Power on targets      -0 --off       Power off targets\n-q --query     Query plug status     -l --list      List available targets\n-c --cycle     Power cycle targets   -r --reset     Reset targets\n-f --flash     Turn beacon on        -u --unflash   Turn beacon off\n-b --beacon    Query beacon status   -n --node      Query node status\n-t --temp      Query temperature     -V --version   Report powerman version\n-D --device    Report device status  -T --telemetry Show device telemetry\n-x --exprange  Expand host ranges\nFailover mds1 to client-23vm3",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 6
